headline: Dell Technologies (NYSE:DELL) Appoints Manish Gupta To Lead India Operations
summary: Dell Technologies (NYSE:DELL) recently announced the appointment of Manish Gupta as the new President and Managing Director for its India operations. Over the last quarter, Dell's stock price surged 24%, largely aligned with favorable market conditions, which saw a 13% rise over the past year.
